   Starting Your Own Business

   If you are considering starting your own business, you have come to the
       right place. The Starting Courses Directory will guide you through
       the critical steps necessary to make your dreams come true. Over 52
       national Women's Business Development Centers have teamed up with
       small business experts to provide you with valuable information and
       insightful advice on how to make your venture a Success. So are you
       ready? Well, let's get started!
